(593, 'Need new wheels, can''t decide/limited knowledge.', 'Hey, guys. I need/want some new wheels, as i''m getting some new ones some time in the future. I will mainly be doing street skating, but i''m not restricted to that only. My trucks are nothing special, they''re just standard trucks. I have 51mm/99A wheels currently. I''ve also heard about Zero having good wheels, but idk.\r\n\r\n\r\nOh yeah, and are Whiskey Militia wheels any good?', 2026, 0, '2013-11-19 13:00:00'),
(594, 'Looking for new wheels', 'It''s between spitfire,gold,momentum or rictas I ride more park than street and I wanna slide but I want the wheel to be grippy', 2028, 0, '2013-12-08 13:00:00'),
(595, 'Bones STF or Formula Four', 'These are the wheels I''m looking at. What would you recommend? They''re around the same price and both at my local store. Which would you buy?', 496, 0, '2013-09-25 13:00:00'),
(596, 'Ricta speed rings VS Spitfire F4', 'Both are 52, the rictas are harder and supposedly don''t squish on landings', 1875, 0, '2013-11-30 13:00:00'),
(601, 'What is Skateboard', 'A skateboard is a type of sports equipment used primarily for the activity of skateboarding. It usually consists of a specially designed maplewood board combined with a polyurethane coating used for making smoother slides and stronger durability.', 1, 2, '2014-05-12 12:19:44');
