(274, 'Quote:\r\nOriginally Posted by Elizabeth\n\r\nim getting this soon just for cruising\r\nand fuck griptape when you have carpet\r\nI just googled it, and that board is like $140-150? For $20-30 more, you can get a much better setup, even if it is just for cruising. Those trucks look pretty weird with the massive bushing seat or whatever that looks like it''d be completely useless, other than to cause washerbite.\r\n\r\nIf you don''t mind a slightly longer board (33in) you''d be much better off with something like this:\r\nhttp://longboardskater.com/mm5/merch...tegory_Code=LY\r\n\r\nor\r\n\r\nhttp://longboardskater.com/mm5/merch...tegory_Code=LY\r\n\r\nBoth of those are ollie-able too.', 406, 186, 1, '2011-05-27 07:30:00'),
