(278, 'How are classic freerides? I need a new pair of wheels and MHS just got 72mm cf. I''ve heard good stuff about abec11 but never tried their classic thane.', 406, 183, 0, '2011-06-04 07:30:00'),
(279, 'Quote:\r\nOriginally Posted by Joshua\nHow are classic freerides? I need a new pair of wheels and MHS just got 72mm cf. I''ve heard good stuff about abec11 but never tried their classic thane.\r\nEasily one of my favorite wheels for soft wheel sliding. They have the smoothest, most buttery slide I''ve ever experienced. They don''t ice out like wheels like Cult Classics either, which is nice. Plus, the thane lines they leave are awesome. The only downside is that they wear down pretty fast.', 406, 186, 1, '2011-06-04 07:30:00'),
