(289, 'I just picked this thing up.\r\n\r\nhttp://www.nhsfunfactory.com/item/11...t-Creep-Cruzer\r\n\r\nI know it''s a very beginner board but I''ll try out some of this stuff and upgrade as I see fit.\r\nI have done a search on the feels and on the trucks but I haven''t found any info on them. I''m pretty sure that since it''s a very inexpensive board that they aren''t the best of quality but some info would be good. How are the bushing for someone 6''2" and 205lbs? What will fit in them, bones Hardcore in stiff is what I was thinking if they fit.\r\nHow about the wheels? I''m not doing any hill bombing really as I haven''t really ridden one so they will be short mild hills so I don''t go to fast until I learn how to slide to a stop.\r\n\r\nThanks guys.', 406, 212, 0, '2011-06-25 07:30:00'),
