(301, 'If i wanted to just cruise and bomb hills on occasion would this be a good setup;\r\n-sector 9 bert pintail deckhttp://store.sector9.com/Product.asp...ECKS&color=RAS\r\n-10 inch gullwing trucks\r\n-69mm 80a 9ball wheels\r\n-reds bearings', 406, 215, 1, '2011-06-28 07:30:00'),
