(310, 'Quote:\r\nOriginally Posted by Maximilian\nLongboarding, or...? If you were longboarding, 27 feet is impressive.\r\nI''ve just started pushing 30ft+ powerslides on soft wheels lately. IMO, the hardest part is committing to it.\r\n\r\nQuote:\r\nOriginally Posted by BSNowner\r\nFuck long boarding its only purpose is to get to point a +b ok i can do that on a regular board stop fucking with the shape and try a zero or dgk right\r\nYou''re fucking ignorant. Longboarding isn''t only about commuting, though pushing on a 70mm+ soft wheel is a lot more efficient than a 52mm 99a wheel. Go bomb a hill and try to hold a line at 40mph on your "regular board."\r\n\r\nIf people didn''t "fuck with shapes," the current shape of your dkg or Zero boards wouldn''t exist. You''d still be on boards like this:', 406, 186, 1, '2011-07-03 07:30:00'),
