(325, 'Alright I browsed through these forums very briefly, but didn''t find any information about this:\r\n\r\nMy father, who just turned 50 began longboarding last year. He owns a pretty awesome Sector 9, and he just began getting into the "Land Paddling" Scene. Basically for those who haven''t heard it is pretty much the equivalent of Stand Up Paddle Surfing.\r\n\r\nSearch Kahuna Creations on Youtube, or through search engine.', 406, 221, 0, '2011-10-23 07:30:00'),
