(2953, 'Oh cool ill prob go with mini logo k-12 first creature sounds promising. After that I gotta try a magenta concave or not those sound great. Always wanted a Dgk but sk8mafia looks great as well lol. I''m gonna skate the hell outta my superior I''m getting for x-mas first.\r\n\r\nAlthough lookin at my superior one with cat in shades :) I swear I think it may be defective, feels like it has more concave on one side I didn''t really notice when I bought it, might be just me tho. Magenta looks so good! Ugh hard choices.', 508, 1108, 0, '2013-12-16 18:30:00'),
(2954, 'DGK has great concave, shape is too pointy for me, but loved the cave.\r\n\r\nAnti-Hero, Bacon and Lurkville (they have a nice deep one if you can find it) are deep.\r\n\r\nPowell K15 = deepshit\r\n\r\nCreature doesn''t seem as deep as they used to be? Still have fat noses.\r\n\r\nDeep''cave is really hard to find these days. I miss the H-Street concave...deepest and steepest you could get.', 508, 445, 0, '2013-12-16 18:30:00'),
