(2956, 'How''s magenta concave? I guess it really doesn''t matter, but yea sucks concave is harder to find now plus I can''t skate 8s, well my chocolate is but the trucks are too small for em.\r\n\r\nSo I guess after my k-12 magenta or dgk it is. Just hard to find 7.75 in dgk. I gotta stop thinkin bout skate decks lmao.', 508, 1108, 0, '2013-12-17 18:30:00'),
(2957, 'I''d been skating a Minilogo K-12 off and on all year. Yeah, it''s got steep concave, but there''s something weird about it. I don''t like how "unstable" my ollies are sometimes. Compared to my Zero P2''s steep concave, the Zero is both steep and much more controllable.\r\n\r\nHabitat and Creature are also steep.', 508, 448, 0, '2013-12-17 18:30:00'),
