(3168, 'eS Anti-Social : Very comfortable. The laces on mine actually lasted about three or so weeks before actually tearing apart. They do rip fast on the side, so if you do a lot of ollies, you''ll notice the wear. They take impact VERY well so good for big drops. They skate like eS Accels\r\n\r\nPros:\r\nGood board feel\r\nComfortable\r\nGood for big stairs or drops\r\n\r\nCons:\r\nTear rather easy\r\nLace protection sucks balls\r\n\r\nOverall : 8/10\r\n\r\neS Accel Plus : Obviously from the look, you can tell they''re just the Accel with a strap. Anyway, they''re really really comfortable. The board feel is so-so, they''re kind of thick on the bottom, however the comfort totally makes up for it. If you like to buy shoes that are too big for you, then the Accel Pluses are for you, as they have a strap. They take impact really well. Durable like hell too if you buy them in leather. The suade rips very easy.\r\n\r\nPros:\r\nDurable\r\nComfortable\r\nGood for big drops or stairs\r\nStrap for extra stability\r\n\r\nCons:\r\nSo-so board feel\r\n\r\nOverall : 9/10\r\n\r\nFallen Patriots : One of my favorite shoes, although I do prefer the Accels. They''re pretty clunky, however the durability makes up for it. The board feel does suck a bit, as the shoes are clunky, as I said. I''ve had mine for about 2 months, and I skate everyday, and they still haven''t actually ripped. They''re very comfortable to walk around in as well. The laces tear very quickly.\r\n\r\nPros:\r\nVERY durable\r\nLook badass\r\nVery comfortable\r\n\r\nCons:\r\nLace protection system sucks hard\r\nClunky\r\nAlmost no board feel\r\n\r\nOverall : 7/10\r\n\r\nVans Rowley XL3 : I love how this shoe is so light-weight. They do tear easy, and the grip isn''t the best, but the lightness is so awesome. I''m skating this shoe and the Patriots currently right now, and the Patriots are holding up way better after 2 months than these at just a couple weeks. The laces are very well protected however and they insole is VERY VERY thick and gooey so it''s very comfortable.\r\n\r\nPros:\r\nVery comfortable\r\nGood for big drops\r\nLace protection system is awesome\r\nVery lightweight\r\nMade of Vegan materials if you''re into that sort of thing\r\n\r\nCons:\r\nThey tear ridiculously easy\r\n\r\nOverall : 7/10', 517, 1227, 0, '2006-04-22 18:30:00'),
