(3214, 'Etnies Bastien- Okay shoe. Grip wears out fast, semi- comfortable, pretty durable. 6/10\r\n\r\nAdio Duke- Horrible shoe. The toe cap butsted the first day, grip wears out in about 2 weeks. Rips very easily. 3/10\r\n\r\n\r\nCirca cx205- my current shoe and favorite so far. The grip isn''t wearing out fast, and the shoe only ripping a little after about a month. The toe cap is very strong. 8/10', 517, 1262, 0, '2006-07-08 18:30:00'),
(3215, 'Nike Zoom Tres- these are probably the best shoes ive ever owned,i have been skating them for about 2 months and theres hardly any sign of wear on the toe cap, and are verry comfortable , and almost impossible to bruise your heel in, the only problem with theweses shoes is that the bottom(while impact softening, flakes off) on a scale of 1-10 i give them a 9.5', 517, 1263, 0, '2006-07-08 18:30:00'),
