(3239, 'Vans Rowley XL III - these shoes have no board feel. they also have relatively squarish toes. they tore up fast and had bad flick 1/10\r\n\r\nEmerica Tilt 2- great shoe. ive had them like a month and a half and they are just starting to tear up. the grip has lasted very well. they have foog flick and board feel 9/10\r\n\r\nEmerica Reynolds 2- another amazing shoe by emerica. i got them used and they lasted another 1 1/2 months (got them from a regular kid who could do nollie flips, im goofy) the toe cap rippid, then the rubber underneath lasted another while longer. great board feel, amazing flick 10/10', 517, 1277, 0, '2006-08-02 18:30:00'),
