(3267, 'Fallen Troopers-\r\nGREAT GRIP, too bad it lasts like 1month and a half =\\. Anyway, the shoe is pretty good, decent board feel, laces rip fast though. Sucky ass ankle support if you ask me, I must''ve hurt my ankle 3-4 times a week. Lasted me 2 1/2 months. Final assessment: I suggest you buy these if there cheap, i paid $70 somthing for the red ones. There deffenitly NOT worth $70, maybe $45-$50.\r\n\r\n\r\nFallen Ace- Wow all I have to say! This shoe has better board feel than the accel and doesn''t rip that quick! I had them litterally 6months+ and loved them. Laces took me about 2 weeks to rip. Suede is the best on these cause after a little while there was a tough as nails rubber underlay. Its tough to rip through, It happend after 5 months then a whole formed so I shoe gooed them. Then they fell apart after that. Final Assesmant: My BEST and favorite shoe! Buy it, I got mie for a cheap price at the shop for like $25, very good boardfeel, crazy laces that take a while to rip, tough shoes, tough shoes!', 517, 1293, 0, '2006-08-31 18:30:00'),
