(3273, 'Lakai Howard 4 limiteds\r\n\r\n\r\nThese shoes are the shit! Got these a month ago for $25 and they''re awesome. The black suade top cap is great! Its worn down and theres ANOTHER toe cap underneath which is plastic! Same thing on the sides. Boardfeel is the best, better the Accels! You feel like your skating in socks! Laces don''t seem to be a problem, I still have the original laces theres only 4 missing out of six. Bad thing, they KILL your feet. If you get them put fallen insole in them or something because your heels get sore after 3 days. I now use them as walking shoes, I wouldn''t recomend them though:\r\n-Great borad feel.\r\n-VERY durable\r\n-Good lacing system, FULL secret lace loop option.\r\n-Takes slams bad', 517, 1293, 0, '2006-09-02 18:30:00'),
