(3361, 'Fallen scouts=BEST SHOE IVE EVER HAD. They lasted me at least 5 or 6 months, great board feel and good impact. They had amazing flick, i could do double flips, varial double flips, fakie double flips etc. in them every try. Also they look great, i really wanted the green leather ones but i could only find the black ones with white sole. Overall, amazing shoe 10/10\r\n\r\nVans No Skool, very grippy, impact was decent, and fairly good board feel. They didnt last long, i had the polka dot ones and the sides are made of canvas. They lasted around 3 months, but they were still pretty good shoes.\r\n7/10\r\n\r\nReynolds 2 i had them in purple and they were damn sexy, over all nice shoe 8/10\r\n\r\nIpath Crickets terrible shoes, i hate them. lasted me around 2 weeks no joke, sole wore down so fast and so did the toe cap. they werent very comfortable they just sucked. complete garbage 0/10', 517, 1343, 0, '2007-04-13 18:30:00'),
(3362, 'Quote:\r\nOriginally Posted by Emmanuel\r\nVans Varial\r\n(my grandma bought me them)\r\n\r\n\r\nFirst Impression:\r\n\r\npros:\r\ngood padding, yet boardfeel is still there\r\ngrippy yet hard sole, for longer wear.\r\ncome with extra laces\r\nI LOVE the way they look.\r\n\r\nCons:\r\nLaces rip easily\r\nWeak suede\r\nsold in khols, famous footwear, etc.\r\n\r\n\r\nafter breaking them in around school and such, I decided it was time to go skate them. Y''know, give my P-rods a break.\r\nFirst thing I thought was that they are Georgeous, in my opinion. The brown really pulls it all together.\r\n\r\nOne small annoying thing that bothers me is that between the gap of the waffle sole and the solid rubber, rocks can get stuck in there, messing up my griptape.\r\n\r\nBig letdown: First day skating, the suede starts ripping. weak. weak weak weak. All i did was ollies and heelflips anyways.\r\nDidn''t expect much, didn''t get much.\r\n\r\ni''ll post a better review later, when they''re destroyed. this was only the first run...\r\ndude i have these. ive skated in these for about 3 weeks and the suade has not ripped yet so i dont know why urs ripped the first day. but the laces do rip easily', 517, 701, 0, '2007-04-13 18:30:00'),
