(3381, 'emerica reynolds 3''s : great shoe, very durable, kickflips wear down the vulc, took 4 months to get ollie hole, only bad thing was sole wore down QUICK.\r\netnies arto 2''s: GREAT shoe, rips very easily though, the sole NEVER wears down, ive had mine 5 months and i just retired them from skating and the sole is still perfect. only buy if you can buy new shoes soon though, with 3 flips theyll have a hole within 2 weeks.\r\nfallen ripper: great shoes, skate great, awesome boardfeel, rip fairly easy, just your average skate shoe. recommend buying it.', 517, 1356, 0, '2007-07-05 18:30:00'),
(3382, 'Circa Adrian Lopez 605-Very good shoe. I''ve had these for over six months and the toecap has just started to rip. Grip stays very well, and has only flattened out a bit. I''ve broken two sets of laces on the left shoe, but thats only because the lace protector has a sharp edge. It probably isn''t like that for all of them. The color fades after about 2 weeks, mostly on your front foot(the one that you would flick with when you do your kickflip) and if you do a lot of flip tricks, there will be white lines on the part of the board that you flicked, but other than that, it is an excellent shoe! I am skating these right now and they''re still gonna last me a while longer. I would definitly recomend getting these if you are ever looking for a new pair of shoes and you see them, and they are also fairly cheap! (I got mine for $65)', 517, 325, 0, '2007-07-18 18:30:00'),
(3383, 'Emerica Kirchart 4\r\n\r\nBoardfeel-\r\nYou can''t feel the board under your feet, I was expecting much more from this shoe 4/10\r\nDurability-\r\nIt doesn''t last very long without shoe goo, The sole rips very quickly, The olle lace protection almost ripped off, and the toe area has been completely destroyed 3/10\r\nGrip-\r\nDoesn''t have too much grip, but has just enough. Ripped incredibly quickly tho 7/10\r\nCushion-\r\nThis is the only reason I like this shoe. The insole is very comfortable, and it cushions most of your tricks and landings. The strap has saved me from messed up ankles alot. 9/10\r\n\r\nOverall 6/10\r\nNot a very good shoe, especially for the price. You can pick up a pair for 40 bucks if you wanna try them, but I don''t recommend it.', 517, 1357, 0, '2007-07-18 18:30:00'),
