(3553, 'Nike SB Blazer: Really good grip, AMAZING board feel, good impact cushioning, Lasted me about 2 months and still havent ripped, and very comfortable.\r\nhttp://www.skateparkoftampa.com/spot...s/23_10764.jpg\r\nReynolds 3: good board feel, impact is not that great, the grip is not that good, the outsole does not last long, and they rip too fast.\r\nhttp://exodus2051.tripod.com/myspace...white-grey.jpg\r\nNike SB dunk low: good grip, outsole is very durable, yet no board feel, and you dont feel any impact.\r\nhttp://www.simplysneakers.com/wp-con...griptape-2.jpg', 517, 1470, 0, '2009-09-20 18:30:00'),
