(3609, 'I have some Adidas shelltoes in light brown nubuck, and they seem to be holding up fine, aside from the laces, of course. I''ve been skating those for about a month, and unlike shelltoes in the past, the sole hasn''t separated from the upper and there are no holes in the upper yet, either. I got those at the Adidas factory outlet here at the mall. I just went and got some new DC Court Graphix in all black the other night, though. I''m still trying to break those in, so the verdict is out on that.', 517, 1497, 0, '2012-10-20 18:30:00'),
