(3618, 'Es Accel- probably known as the or one of the best skate shoes ever, i had 3 pairs they all were very comfy nice padding around the heel an tongue area, had amazing board feel very light weight as well, they hold up forever to. the toe cap area somewhat gives out quicker with the suede ones but ghe leather last longer an the soles don''t wear out to quick. if Es were ever to bring these back i would never buy any other shoes again.\r\n\r\n2. Es Accel plus- same description as above but with a strap would deff buy these again as well.\r\n\r\n3. Emerica Reynold 2s- fav Emerica shoe ever gripped really well nice padding all the way around, sick look an design. They held up for months the soles got smooth before the toe cap got ripped an what not wouldn''t mind these again.\r\n\r\n\r\n4. DC PJ Ladd sig- currently skating these an man', 517, 1501, 0, '2013-09-26 18:30:00'),
