(4825, 'Quote:\r\nOriginally Posted by Patrick\nYou like mf doom too? one thing we can agree on...\r\n\r\nAs for the send helps, I can''t see any imprefections on the one you posted. I dunno, and if they are fake whats the big deal? Do they really not last long at all if they are fake?\r\nif they were fakes. a couple of things. one people would laugh at you when they notice they are fake. two us sb-c people will hate you and three they wont last that long because theres no quality control for them. just the worst case scenario i can think of. the verdict is DONT BUY FAKES.\r\n\r\nfor real send helps, you get compliments from people, you experience a smile in your face eveytime you wear them and skate.', 518, 1333, 0, '2006-09-15 18:30:00'),
(4826, 'Quote:\r\nOriginally Posted by Juda\r\nif they were fakes. a couple of things. one people would laugh at you when they notice they are fake. two us sb-c people will hate you and three they wont last that long because theres no quality control for them. just the worst case scenario i can think of. the verdict is DONT BUY FAKES.\r\n\r\nfor real send helps, you get compliments from people, you experience a smile in your face eveytime you wear them and skate.\r\nWho the hell examines someones elses shoes to see if they are fake? how do you even tell if they are fake? I don''t think I know anyone like that. I might just get fakes purposfully so save money.', 518, 1592, 0, '2006-09-15 18:30:00'),
(4827, 'You can brag about price with legits. How weird will this sound to your friends: "Yea they usually go for around $250-300, but I got them for $70."\r\n\r\nas they fall apart. All my shit is legit :)', 518, 627, 0, '2006-09-16 18:30:00'),
(4828, 'Fakes fall apart so fast, my friend gave me some fake Hawaiis and they were horrible.', 518, 821, 0, '2006-09-16 18:30:00'),
(4829, 'Quote:\r\nOriginally Posted by Patrick\nWho the hell examines someones elses shoes to see if they are fake? how do you even tell if they are fake? I don''t think I know anyone like that. I might just get fakes purposfully so save money.\r\nFakes are bad because they do fall apart easily, again, they are made by someone in his basement, so they aren''t made with the same high quality of a kid in indonesia. I tried on a pair of my friends fakes, they were real flimsy and uncomfortable too. No one is going to notice your shoes are fake, unless they are a real SB collector and stares at your shoes for 10 minutes.\r\n\r\nIt''s not that fakes are just SBs not made by nike. The main reasons are.\r\n\r\n1. Your money isen''t going into skateboarding, it''s going into some guys pocket.\r\n\r\n2. The more fakes people buy, the more fakes people sell, and the level of fakes, grows and grows....\r\n\r\n3. On your actual shoe, it will most likely fall apart easily, it could have miscolors, the glue is usually the worst.\r\n\r\nAnyways, I''m not stopping you from buying them, I''m just giving you a heads up, not all fakes are horrible quality, but its the fact that my money isen''t going into the skateboarding industry that gets me.\r\n\r\nAgain, do as you please, just looking out for you and anyone else buying off ebay.', 518, 1507, 0, '2006-09-16 18:30:00'),
(4830, 'yea, usually if the price is too good to be true, they are fake. that being said, there are some legit collectable dunk lows and p-rods and shit for only $150', 518, 627, 0, '2006-09-16 18:30:00'),
