(11019, 'Shit i wish i saw the 8$ tensors, i already got some maglite uber blocks, had to send them back and get new ones because they were defective but i tested out my friends pair on my organika board and i freaking loved them. I''m using indys right now and idk, they feel a lot better for cruising and they seem more durable but the tensors seemed to have better balance and, not to go crazy over weight, they were so light, it doesn''t make me able to do anything i can''t with the indys, but any trick i do feels smoother.\r\n\r\nBTW Kayo decks are waaaaay too good. dwindle was more comfortable but nowhere near as fun (dat organika deck pop). Sticking with kayo from now on.', 542, 1124, 0, '2014-01-23 18:30:00'),
