(11056, 'I like trucks to be the same width as the board or up to a quarter inch wider. Narrower bothers me for some reason. I have 8.0 on my 8.0, 8.38 on my 8.25 board and am about to order up 8.75 trucks with an 8.5 board. If I were to build up a 7.81 I would put 8" trucks (139s) on it.', 546, 1094, 0, '2014-03-23 18:30:00'),
