(11156, 'If you don''t have them, your trucks will wiggle all over the place, and make a horrid clicking noise. Pick up some pivot cups asap.\r\n\r\nYou can try contacting Globe and tell them what happened. I told Indy my pivot cups shredded (which was true) and they shipped me a bunch with some stickers for free.', 550, 259, 0, '2014-02-24 18:30:00'),
