(11195, 'Quote:\r\nOriginally Posted by Macey\nHi i received for christmas a set of Tensor 5.5 that match perfectly my 8.25 deck, I don''t know why but something inside me pushed me to buy a set of new thunder 149. Trying to feel more stable. I don''t want to change size of my board, probably just go with an 8.3. So Yesterday i bought them from an online shop, but now i think it was a stupid. What do you guys think does 149 fit my deck and also do you think i made the right choice changing from Tensor to Thunder?? And does a changing from 5.5 to 149 will affect my flip tricks?\r\nthank you for your answer!\r\nSell the Tensors on ebay or amazon, ride the 149s on an 8.25" like millions of skaters (and most of the real team).', 556, 445, 0, '2014-02-03 18:30:00'),
