(11198, 'I like the Tensors I have. I''ll admit they do feel a little weird compared to what I was skating back in the day (Indys, Gullwing, G&S) but I got used to it. As for weight and controlling flip just remember it''s more about finesse than strength. You just need to lighten your touch and cut out unnecessary movements.', 556, 466, 0, '2014-02-03 18:30:00'),
