(11207, 'I think they''d be alright if you''re just planning on cruising, but I''d tend not to trust ebay. I suggest looking on an actual skate site and looking in the Longboard/ Cruiser section.', 561, 1093, 0, '2014-04-28 18:30:00'),
(11208, 'http://www.ebay.com/itm/ACE-55-SKATE...item4ad330049a\r\nhttp://www.ebay.com/itm/BIGFOOT-Long...item5afe1eb275\r\nI would get something like that. If your looking for a surfing feel, I would get 68mm at the absolute smallest, Hell I ride 60mm on my street skateboard!\r\nAlso, I''ve ordered from TGM before, and I know they are a trustworthy company.', 561, 266, 0, '2014-04-28 18:30:00'),
