(11217, 'Half the time, I ride Spitfire Meltdowns 56mm 80HD wheels. Which is pretty much the same thing. Of course you can ollie. You can powerslide too with a little force. You can pretty much do most tricks that don''t involve sliding wheels.\r\n\r\nAre you afraid of the size or the durometer?', 564, 448, 0, '2014-04-28 18:30:00'),
