(11571, 'I haven''t tried the Formula Four''s, but I have the Bones STF wheels and they''re great!', 595, 516, 0, '2013-10-22 18:30:00'),
(11572, 'F4''s!', 595, 1998, 0, '2013-11-10 18:30:00'),
(11573, 'I''ve had plenty pairs of STF''s now I will agree these are a solid choice but been rocking formula fours for a while now and I power slide alot around these cali hills and never get dem flat spots. I''m actually buying a new pair tomorrow hopefully. I''d go formula fours.', 595, 460, 0, '2013-11-10 18:30:00'),
(11574, 'buy one now and when that set wears buy the other....', 595, 469, 0, '2013-11-12 18:30:00'),
