(11576, 'Spit fire Formula Fours for sure', 595, 1495, 0, '2013-11-12 18:30:00'),
(11577, 'formula fours', 595, 1933, 0, '2013-11-15 18:30:00'),
(11578, 'Bones STF''s guaranteed will last a long time, they''re really hard and they don''t have as much variety in the graphics dept. - if that''s what matters to you. From what others are saying though, I''m kinda interested in the SF Formula Fours just to try something new.\r\n\r\n* STF''s does have some variety but Spit Fire has nicer graphics imo.', 595, 490, 0, '2013-12-05 18:30:00');
